data.title: What day of the week was January 1, 1969?
data.meta_description: Get the day of the week for January 1, 1969?
data.text:
The day of the week January 1st, 1969 fell on was a Wednesday.

Morris Chestnut the American actor was born on 01 January in 1969. As was Nicolle Dickson the Australian actress , Melissa DiMarco the Canadian actress and producer , Paul Lawrie the Scottish golfer , Christi Paul the American journalist , Verne Troyer the American actor and stuntman .
